          "44 university students",
          "None Applicable",
          "LMS logs, Peripheral Data, Eye-Tracking",
          "None Specified",
          "[Orientation, Planning, Monitoring, Evaluation, First-reading, Re-reading, Elaboration/Organization]",
          "Highighed Features are MicroSRL processes identified by the iauthors from the data. The table also includes common transitions.\n\nAuthors use a trace parcer to identify relevant transitions and identify sequences of actions that are fully connected from sequences where some of the expected actions are not fulfilled. ",
          "Fuzzy Miner",
          "-",
          "-",
          "Using the Disconnected method, Monitoring seemed disconnected from all other SRL processes.\n\nOn the Connected perspective, all metacognitive processes seemed to occur simultaneously and ocuppying the “same space”. \n\n",
          "Trace parsing methods have a significant impact on the identification of SRL processes from log data. \n\nDisconnected methods may over-isolate some processes.",
          "Authors perform a comparison of different types of trace parsing methods.\n\n",
          "The effectiveness of Trace Parsing methods is yet to be fully discovered.\n\nRequires more data and additional educational contexts."
        ]
      ],
